Kopaliny is a &lt;a href="village"&gt;village&lt;/a&gt; in the administrative district of &lt;a href="Gmina%20Nowy%20Wi%C5%9Bnicz"&gt;Gmina Nowy Wiśnicz&lt;/a&gt;, within &lt;a href="Bochnia%20County"&gt;Bochnia County&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Lesser%20Poland%20Voivodeship"&gt;Lesser Poland Voivodeship&lt;/a&gt;, in southern Poland. It lies approximately north of &lt;a href="Nowy%20Wi%C5%9Bnicz"&gt;Nowy Wiśnicz&lt;/a&gt;, south of &lt;a href="Bochnia"&gt;Bochnia&lt;/a&gt;, and east of the regional capital &lt;a href="Krak%C3%B3w"&gt;Kraków&lt;/a&gt;.
